Description:
    This generator creates the service file based on Lesli conventions according to the path given.

Example:
    bin/rails generate lesli_services core/things

    This will create:
        /app/services/thing_services.rb
    
    bin/rails generate lesli_services core/users

    This will create:
        /app/services/user_services.rb

    bin/rails generate lesli_services cloud_shared/projects

    This will create:
        /engines/cloud_shared/app/services/cloud_shared/project_services.rb
    
    bin/rails generate lesli_services lesli_cloud/accounts

    This will create:
        /engines/lesli_cloud/app/services/lesli_cloud/account_services.rb

